## Workflow

### 1. Make Changes
- Read @PROJECT_CONTEXT.md
- Modify code
- Test in Godot

### 2. Document
Update CHANGELOG.md:
```markdown
## [Unreleased]

### Changed
- FileX: Description (line 123)
```

### 3. Commit (Local)
```bash
git add .
git commit -m "feat: Description"
```

### 4. Report (Telegram → Atlas)
```
✅ [Claude Code 작업 완료]

📝 작업: ...
📂 파일: ...
✅ 테스트: Godot 확인 완료
📌 Git: 로컬 커밋 완료 (push 대기)
```

### 5. Wait for Approval
- Git push: Wait for Steve's "OK"
- Notion update: Wait for Steve's "OK"

