## Quick Reference

### File Paths
- Scripts: `res://scripts/`, `res://autoload/`
- UI Screens: `res://ui/screens/`
- UI Components: `res://ui/components/`

### Colors (UITheme)
- bg: Dark blue `(0.1, 0.1, 0.18, 1)`
- panel: Dark purple `(0.15, 0.15, 0.25, 1)`
- primary: Blue `(0.48, 0.62, 0.94, 1)`
- accent: Gold `(0.98, 0.71, 0.25, 1)`

### Layout
- Resolution: 390×844
- TopBar: 60px (if exists)
- BottomNav: 60px at y=784
- Content: 0-784 (or 60-784)

---

## Common Patterns

### New Screen
```gdscript
extends Control

"""
ScreenName - Brief description
"""

@onready var button = $Button

func _ready():
    _setup_ui()
    _connect_signals()

func _setup_ui() -> void:
    UITheme.apply_button_style(button, "primary")

func _connect_signals() -> void:
    button.pressed.connect(_on_button_pressed)

func _on_button_pressed() -> void:
    pass
```

### Using GameManager
```gdscript
var gold = GameManager.get_gold()
GameManager.add_gold(50)
var nodes = GameManager.get_dream_nodes()
```

